# Shared local environment template for agents working in this prototypes hub.
# Copy to .env.local only for local development. Do not commit real secrets.
#
# Production and preview secrets should live in Vercel Environment Variables.
# To hydrate local credentials from Vercel after linking the project, run:
#   vercel env pull .env.local

# Example:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
